TITLE: Core Sway Standard Library Components
DESCRIPTION: The prelude's core components including Address, ContractId, Identity, Vec, StorageMap, Option, Result, assert, revert, log, and msg_sender. These components are automatically imported into every Sway program and provide essential functionality for blockchain development.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FuelLabs/sway/blob/master/docs/reference/src/documentation/misc/prelude.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sway
CODE:
```
Address      // A struct containing a b256 value for wallet addresses
ContractId   // A struct containing a b256 value for contract IDs
Identity     // An enum containing Address & ContractID structs
Vec          // A growable, heap-allocated vector
StorageMap   // A key-value mapping in contract storage
Option       // An enum containing Some<T> or None
Result       // An enum representing Ok or Err states
assert       // Functions for condition verification
revert       // Functions for reverting execution
log          // Function for logging arbitrary stack types
msg_sender   // Function to get the calling Identity
```

