TITLE: Implementing swap Function in Sway
DESCRIPTION: This function performs a token swap in the liquidity pool. It calculates the output amount based on the constant product formula and updates the pool balances.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FuelLabs/sway/blob/master/docs/reference/src/documentation/examples/liquidity-pool.md#2025-04-17_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: Sway
CODE:
```
fn swap(pool: LiquidityPool, token1_in: u64, token2_out: u64) -> (LiquidityPool, u64) {
    let k = pool.token1_balance * pool.token2_balance;
    let new_token2_balance = pool.token2_balance - token2_out;
    let new_token1_balance = k / new_token2_balance;
    let token1_in_required = new_token1_balance - pool.token1_balance;

    assert(token1_in >= token1_in_required, "Insufficient input amount");

    LiquidityPool {
        token1_balance: new_token1_balance,
        token2_balance: new_token2_balance,
        liquidity_tokens: pool.liquidity_tokens,
    },
    token2_out
}
```

