TITLE: Defining Supertraits in Sway
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create supertraits, where one trait requires functionality from another trait.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FuelLabs/sway/blob/master/docs/book/src/advanced/traits.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: sway
CODE:
```
trait Eq {
    fn equals(self, b: Self) -> bool;
}

trait Ord: Eq {
    fn gte(self, b: Self) -> bool;
}

impl Ord for u64 {
    fn gte(self, b: Self) -> bool {
        // As `Eq` is a supertrait of `Ord`, `Ord` can access the equals method
        self.equals(b) || self.gt(b)
    }
}
```

