TITLE: Converting to Byte Arrays in Sway
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to convert various types to byte arrays in Sway using functions from the bytes_conversions module. This allows for serialization of different types to a consistent byte representation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FuelLabs/sway/blob/master/docs/book/src/basics/converting_types.md#2025-04-17_snippet_15

