TITLE: Implementing a Target Contract for Upgradeable Proxy in Sway
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows an implementation contract that can be used with the proxy contract. It includes a function to double an input value and update storage, demonstrating how upgradeable contracts work in Sway.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FuelLabs/sway/blob/master/docs/book/src/blockchain-development/external_code.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sway
CODE:
