TITLE: Implementing Counter Contract in Sway
DESCRIPTION: A simple counter contract implementation in Sway, including methods to initialize and increment the counter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FuelLabs/sway/blob/master/docs/book/src/testing/testing-with-rust.md#2025-04-17_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: sway
CODE:
```
contract;

storage {
    counter: u64 = 0,
}

abi MyContract {
    #[storage(read, write)]
    fn initialize_counter(value: u64) -> u64;

    #[storage(read, write)]
    fn increment_counter(amount: u64) -> u64;
}

impl MyContract for Contract {
    #[storage(read, write)]
    fn initialize_counter(value: u64) -> u64 {
        storage.counter = value;
        value
    }

    #[storage(read, write)]
    fn increment_counter(amount: u64) -> u64 {
        storage.counter += amount;
        storage.counter
    }
}
```

