TITLE: Usage of forc deploy command for Fuel contract deployment
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the basic usage of the 'forc deploy' command, including its options and arguments. It demonstrates how to deploy a contract, specify a node URL, set gas parameters, and provide contract arguments.
