```
# forc deploy

Usage: forc deploy [OPTIONS] [CONTRACT_ID]

Arguments:
  [CONTRACT_ID]  Contract ID to deploy

Options:
      --node <NODE_URL>            Node URL to deploy to [default: beta-3.fuel.network]
      --gas-price <GAS_PRICE>      Gas price for deployment
      --gas-limit <GAS_LIMIT>      Gas limit for deployment
      --maturity <MATURITY>        Set maturity of the transaction
      --salt <SALT>                Provide a salt to randomize contract ID
      --unsigned                   Generate a transaction request for remote signing
  -s, --signed <SIGNED_TX>         Path to a JSON file containing a signed transaction
      --params <PARAMS>            Provide contract arguments
      --pkg-path <PKG_PATH>        Path to the Forc.toml project manifest [default: .]
  -o, --output <OUTPUT>            Output destination for the compiled contract
      --network <NETWORK>          Configure the network to use
      --realm-client-id <REALM>    The Realm client ID (optional)
  -h, --help                       Print help
```

